      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.2052382109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ごめんなさい。{user}さんと\n二人きりで話すのは久しぶりだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sorry. It's just that talking with you‚ {user} san‚\none on one… It's been a while‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1666663964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 16.6432200866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ついほっぺたが緩んじゃって、えへへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My cheeks just loosened up‚ hehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6432200866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.852789811
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "最近のサニピはみんな忙しくて\n話す時間もなかなか取れないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ everyone in Sunny Peace has been so busy‚\nand it's hard to find time to talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2861231443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今も仕事と仕事の合間に休憩しているだけで\nすぐ移動しないといけないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even now‚ I'm just taking a break between jobs‚\nand I'll have to move soon…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2861236529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.8194580035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも忙しいのはいいことですよね！\nこの後のお仕事も頑張りますよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But being busy is a good thing‚ right?\nI'll do my best in the upcoming work too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333350976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今日のさくらはやる気がみなぎっているな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ you're full of motivation today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0260565556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.0260596074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　今度のイベントで麻奈さんの曲を歌うことが\n決まって、気持ちがどんどん高まってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I'm getting more and more excited because\nI'll be singing Mana-san's song at the next event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3333381494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "しかも琴乃ちゃん達と一緒に歌えるなんて\n想像しただけでワクワクが止まりません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I can't contain my excitement at the thought of\nsinging with Kotono-chan and the others!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5000058334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.3282823996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらと琴乃が麻奈の曲をどんな風に歌うのか\n俺も楽しみだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to how Sakura and\nKotono will sing Mana's song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1232823567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 63.8949490663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、私も楽しみです！　あ、でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm looking forward to it too! Oh‚ but…",
